org.sql: SELECT projects.* FROM projects WHERE projects.lft >= 1 AND projects.rgt <= 10 AND projects.status = 1 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'issue_tracking') IS NOT NULL AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (6, 13)) AND projects.id IN (SELECT DISTINCT project_id FROM projects_trackers) ORDER BY projects.lft ASC
